sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Staff as Event Staff
    participant Scanner as BarcodeScannerScreen
    participant Event as EventScreen
    participant Repo as FirebaseStudentRepository
    participant RTDB as Firebase RTDB
    participant Flow as AttendanceFlowService
    participant Hive as Hive Attendees

    Staff->>Scanner: Scan QR code
    Scanner->>Event: onScanned(rollNo)
    Event->>Event: normalize and cooldown check

    alt Invalid or blocked
        Event-->>Scanner: blocked or invalid result
    else Continue
        Event->>Event: check in-memory student cache
        alt Cache miss
            Event->>Repo: getByRollNumber(rollNo)
            Repo->>RTDB: read studentsByRoll/{rollNo}
            RTDB-->>Repo: student profile or null
            Repo-->>Event: resolved student profile
        else Cache hit
            Event-->>Event: reuse cached profile
        end

        Event->>Event: resolve entry or exit action
        Event->>Flow: recordAttendance(...)
        Flow->>Hive: add or save attendee
        Hive-->>Flow: persisted attendee
        Flow-->>Event: success or blocked result
        Event-->>Scanner: success or blocked message
        Scanner-->>Staff: haptic plus visual feedback
    end
